    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "23. Un Serugs dsihtwoja pehz\nto/ kad wiꞥſch to Naöru btj dsem-\ndinajis / diwſints Gaddus /\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "24. Un Naörs dsihtwoja din-\ndefmits un dewix Gaddus / u-\ndsemdinaja to Tahrn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "25. Un Naörs dsihtwoja peh-\nto / kad wiꞥſch ko Tahrn bi-\ndsemdinajis / ſints diwdefmit-\nun dewix Gaddus / un dsemd-\nnaja Dehlus un Meitas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "26. Un Tahrus dsihtwoja tep-\ntindeſmitsGaddus/un dsemdina-\nja Ahbramu/ Naöru un Ahranu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "27. Un ſchee irr Tahrus Rad-\ndu-Rakſil: Tahrum dſimme Ah-\nbrams/ Naörs un Ahrans / u-\nAhranam dſimme Lats.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "28. Bet Ahrans nomirr\npreeſſch ſawa Tehwa Tahrus\nfawa dſintā Semmē / eekſch u-\nto Kaldeënu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "29. Un Ahbrams un Naöre\napnehmahs Seewas / Ahbrams\nSeewas Wahrs bija Sarāi/ u-\nNaöra Seewas Wahrs bija\nMilka/ Ahrana Meita. Milka\nTehwa un Jiskas Tehwa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "30. Un Sarāi bija neaugliga\nun wiꞥſſai netva Behrnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "31. Un Tahrus nehme Ahbra-\nmu ſawn Dehlu / un Lattu t-\nDehlu Ahrana ſawa Dehla Deh-\nlu/ un to Sarāi ſawn Weddekli\nAhbrama ſawa Dehla Seewu\nun tsgahje ar teem no Ur to Ka-\ndeërnu/ ka tas eetu uhs to Sen-\nmi Kanāān / un tee nahze lihd\nAhranam/ un mahjoja tur.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "32. Un Tahrus Deenas bij-\ndiwſints un peezi Gaddi / u-\nTahrus nomirre Ahranā.\n"
